             was indicted for <rs id="t18080113-10-off54" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080113-10-off54" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080113-10-off54" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               that he on the <rs id="t18080113-10-cd55" type="crimeDate">5th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080113-10-off54 t18080113-10-cd55"></join> in the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080113-10-victim135" type="victimName">
                           Arthur 
                           Windus
                        <interp inst="t18080113-10-victim135" type="surname" value="Windus"></interp>
